Texts.Eng: A ceramic basin produced in the Mantizi style.

Texts.Chs: 非常优雅的脸盆。银河帝国的上层地壳会为它的秘密而杀人。
Texts.Eng: A very elegant basin. The upper crust of the Galactic Empire would kill for its secrets.

Texts.Chs: 做得很好的脸盆。装饰很简单，但优雅到了极点。
Texts.Eng: A very well-made washbasin. The decoration is simple, yet elegant to a fault.

Texts.Chs: 虽然这个脸盆很漂亮，但电子人不需要在里面洗。
Texts.Eng: As beautiful as this basin is, Glitch won't need to wash in it.

Texts.Chs: 虽然这个脸盆很漂亮，但我们伍基人更喜欢更华丽、更引人注目的东西。
Texts.Eng: As pretty as this basin is, we Wookiees prefer something more ornate and eye-catching.

Texts.Chs: 克鲁西斯说，这是一个豪华的盆地。
Texts.Eng: By Kluex, this is one sumptuous basin.

Texts.Chs: 超重行李。当溪流和绿洲丰富时，托格鲁塔就不需要这些东西了。
Texts.Eng: Excess baggage. Togruta do not need such objects when streams and oases are aplenty.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人不需要在Basssin洗衣服！
Texts.Eng: Floran no need to wash in bassssin!

Texts.Chs: 我不认为这个脸盆能在一个小房间里保存下来，这个小房间里有很多小猫咪。
Texts.Eng: I don't think this basin would survive in a small room with a very large littler of Felinlings.

Texts.Chs: 我怀疑大多数猿族能买得起这样的东西只是为了洗自己。
Texts.Eng: I doubt that most Apex could afford to buy something like this just to wash themselves.

Texts.Chs: 我相信我们的祖先曾经创造过这样的东西...
Texts.Eng: I'm sure our forefathers produced something like this once ...

Texts.Chs: 它看起来很美，但我们伊索人却不可能做到。
Texts.Eng: It is beautiful to look at, yet impossible for us Ithorians to make.

Texts.Chs: 只是一个粘土盆...没必要这么激动。
Texts.Eng: It's just some clay basin ... no need to get so excited about it.

Texts.Chs: 这里什么也看不见，只有一个普通的脚盆。
Texts.Eng: Nothin' to see here, just a plain ol' foot-tub.

Texts.Chs: 奇怪的船。不是耳廓狐。非常不寻常！
Texts.Eng: Strange vessel. Not Fenerox. Very unusual!

Texts.Chs: 这个盆地显然不是鲛人的，因为它不够微妙。
Texts.Eng: This basin is clearly not Hylotl, for it is insufficiently subtle.
